short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extends the compatibility of Flowfinitee on Chromium-based browsers so that URLs of active tabs can be detected.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension offers URL detection support for Chromium-based browsers with the Flowfinitee desktop application for better insights into your time expenditure.
